    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Open, variously shaped containers of wood, metal or other rigid material with a flat bottom and a low rim for holding, carrying, or exhibiting articles.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
